-800x686.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-black-kitchen-with-island-081124-1050-15-768x658.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-black-kitchen-with-island-081124-1050-15-1536x1317.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1201\" height=\"1800\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-black-kitchen-081124-1050-16.jpg\" alt=\"Above this modern black kitchen, large glazed openings act as a clerestory and flood the space with diffuse natural light, framing views of the surrounding treetops.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-black-kitchen-081124-1050-16.jpg 1201w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-black-kitchen-081124-1050-16-940x1409.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-black-kitchen-081124-1050-16-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-black-kitchen-081124-1050-16-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-black-kitchen-081124-1050-16-1025x1536.jpg 1025w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1201px) 100vw, 1201px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eBack in the foyer, a floating staircase and cedar-clad volume define the separation between public and private spaces.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1440\" height=\"1800\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/black-and-wood-modern-stairs-081124-1045-18.jpg\" alt=\"A floating staircase and cedar-clad volume define the separation between public and private spaces in this home.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/black-and-wood-modern-stairs-081124-1045-18.jpg 1440w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/black-and-wood-modern-stairs-081124-1045-18-940x1175.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/black-and-wood-modern-stairs-081124-1045-18-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/black-and-wood-modern-stairs-081124-1045-18-768x960.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/black-and-wood-modern-stairs-081124-1045-18-1229x1536.jpg 1229w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1201\" height=\"1800\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/black-and-wood-modern-stairs-081124-1045-19.jpg\" alt=\"A floating staircase and cedar-clad volume define the separation between public and private spaces in this home.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/black-and-wood-modern-stairs-081124-1045-19.jpg 1201w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/black-and-wood-modern-stairs-081124-1045-19-940x1409.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/black-and-wood-modern-stairs-081124-1045-19-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/black-and-wood-modern-stairs-081124-1045-19-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/black-and-wood-modern-stairs-081124-1045-19-1025x1536.jpg 1025w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1201px) 100vw, 1201px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1440\" height=\"1800\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/black-and-wood-modern-stairs-081124-1045-20.jpg\" alt=\"A floating staircase and cedar-clad volume define the separation between public and private spaces in this home.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/black-and-wood-modern-stairs-081124-1045-20.jpg 1440w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/black-and-wood-modern-stairs-081124-1045-20-940x1175.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/black-and-wood-modern-stairs-081124-1045-20-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/black-and-wood-modern-stairs-081124-1045-20-768x960.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/black-and-wood-modern-stairs-081124-1045-20-1229x1536.jpg 1229w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eUp the stairs, a small library with floating shelves blends into the wall.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1733\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-reading-area-black-accent-walls-081124-1047-17.jpg\" alt=\"A small library with floating shelves that blend into the wall.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-reading-area-black-accent-walls-081124-1047-17.jpg 1800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-reading-area-black-accent-walls-081124-1047-17-940x905.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-reading-area-black-accent-walls-081124-1047-17-800x770.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-reading-area-black-accent-walls-081124-1047-17-768x739.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-reading-area-black-accent-walls-081124-1047-17-1536x1479.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn the home’s private areas, like in the primary bedroom, wood floors replace concrete, but stay true to the minimalist intent of the design.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1440\" height=\"1800\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-bedroom-black-accent-wall-081124-1046-21.jpg\" alt=\"In the private areas of this modern home, like in the primary bedroom, wood floors replace concrete, but stay true to the minimalist intent of the design.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-bedroom-black-accent-wall-081124-1046-21.jpg 1440w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-bedroom-black-accent-wall-081124-1046-21-940x1175.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-bedroom-black-accent-wall-081124-1046-21-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-bedroom-black-accent-wall-081124-1046-21-768x960.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-bedroom-black-accent-wall-081124-1046-21-1229x1536.jpg 1229w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn the bathroom, a sculptural, custom concrete floating tub is placed in the center of the bathroom, while a steam shower is available behind.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1800\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-bathroom-bathtub-081124-1046-22.jpg\" alt=\"In the bathroom, a sculptural, custom concrete floating tub is placed in the center of the bathroom, while a steam shower is available behind.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-bathroom-bathtub-081124-1046-22.jpg 1800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-bathroom-bathtub-081124-1046-22-940x940.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-bathroom-bathtub-081124-1046-22-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-bathroom-bathtub-081124-1046-22-200x200.jpg 200w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-bathroom-bathtub-081124-1046-22-768x768.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-bathroom-bathtub-081124-1046-22-1536x1536.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1201\" height=\"1800\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-bathroom-bathtub-081124-1046-23.jpg\" alt=\"In the bathroom, a sculptural, custom concrete floating tub is placed in the center of the bathroom, while a steam shower is available behind.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-bathroom-bathtub-081124-1046-23.jpg 1201w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-bathroom-bathtub-081124-1046-23-940x1409.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-bathroom-bathtub-081124-1046-23-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-bathroom-bathtub-081124-1046-23-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-bathroom-bathtub-081124-1046-23-1025x1536.jpg 1025w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1201px) 100vw, 1201px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eHere’s a look at the floor plan for the home.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2532\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-floor-plan-081124-1052-25.jpg\" alt=\"The floor plan of a modern home.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-floor-plan-081124-1052-25.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-floor-plan-081124-1052-25-940x1240.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-floor-plan-081124-1052-25-800x1055.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-floor-plan-081124-1052-25-768x1013.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-floor-plan-081124-1052-25-1165x1536.jpg 1165w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-floor-plan-081124-1052-25-1553x2048.jpg 1553w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003ePhotography by Rafael Gamo | Architect: Worrell Yeung — Jejon Yeung and Max Worrell, partners; Yunchao Li | Engineers: Silman (structural); Kolb Heating + Cooling (mechanical); PWGC (civil) | Consultants: Sweetbay Landscape Design (landscape) | General Contractor: Fifth and Dune\u003c/h6\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
